Title: One If By Land
Plot: The hostility mounts between the citizens of Jericho and New Bern. A handful of residents of New Bern are shot and injured after getting caught trying to steal from the Jericho salt mine.
GuestStars: Ryan Coughlin, David Meunier, Dustin Seavey, Chet Grissom, Dan Sachoff, Joseph Bucaro
